    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 15 min, remove the potato tray[s] from the oven and crush with the base of a mug to flatten them</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced pepper</strong> to the tray with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>–<strong> </strong>these are your <strong>smashed potatoes & pepper</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven along with the <strong>meat-free empanadas</strong> for 18-20 min or until the potatoes are crisp and golden and the pastry is golden and cooked through</p>",
