    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free empanadas</strong> with the <strong>smashed potatoes & pepper</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the smashed potatoes with the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), then drizzle with some of the <strong>chimichurri sauce</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining chimichurri sauce</strong> to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
